---
---
<section id="world" class="py-32 bg-zinc-950 border-t border-zinc-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">The Visual Lore</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Ashbend is built to be a canvas. The engine drives the logic, but the presentation layer turns it into a vivid, atmospheric experience.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-[4/3] bg-zinc-900">
                <img src="/assets/dawn_after_tasks.jpg" alt="Dawn in Ashbend" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-zinc-950 via-zinc-950/20 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Dawn Over Ashbend</h3>
                    <p class="text-zinc-300 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 delay-100">Every morning brings new schedules, new gossip, and new consequences.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-[4/3] bg-zinc-900">
                <img src="/assets/bridge_whisper.jpg" alt="Bridge Whisper" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-zinc-950 via-zinc-950/20 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">The Bridge Secrets</h3>
                    <p class="text-zinc-300 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 delay-100">NPCs whisper when out of earshot. What you don't hear can still hurt you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="md:col-span-2 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-[21/9] bg-zinc-900">
                <img src="/assets/garden_morning.jpg" alt="Garden Morning" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-70 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-700 group-hover:scale-105" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-zinc-950 via-zinc-950/20 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 p-8 max-w-2xl transform translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform">
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">The Living Ecosystem</h3>
                    <p class="text-zinc-300 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 delay-100">Characters move physically through the space to accomplish their goals. The village feels alive because it physically simulates every tick.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
